name: sy_pnum
notes: Number of transiting planets (as of May 1, 2023)

name: evol
notes: Stellar evolutionary stage (Main Sequence or Sub-Giant)

name: st_limbdark1_derived
notes: First quadratic limb darkening parameter (derived - see MacDougall et al. 2023a)

name: st_limbdark2_derived
notes: Second quadratic limb darkening parameter (derived - see MacDougall et al. 2023a)

name: specmatch_flag
notes: Flag indicating which SpecMatch algorithm was used to derived stellar inputs (Empirical or Synthetic)
